rollback;

explain basic
merge into v2 t1 using (select * from tp2 where c1 = 1) t2 on (t1.c1 = t2.c1) when matched then update set t1.c2 = t2.c1 + 100
when not matched then insert values (t2.c1, t2.c2, t2.c3);
